    <item>
      <title>甚至在米莱的休克疗法开始之前，阿根廷经济就在第四季度下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/argentina-s-economy-slumped-in-fourth-quarter-even-before-milei-s-shock-therapy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷经济在第四季度出现萎缩，巩固了全年的负增长，甚至在即将上任的总统哈维尔·米莱削减支出作为休克疗法的一部分之前也是如此。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/argentina-s-economy-slumped-in-fourth-quarter-even-before-milei-s-shock-therapy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 19:16:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔：通胀有所缓解，但仍过高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-20/powell-inflation-has-eased-but-it-s-still-too-high-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在华盛顿对记者表示，通胀“在过去一年明显放缓，但仍高于我们 2% 的长期目标”。 FOMC 将基准联邦基金利率维持在 5.25% 至 5.5% 的范围内。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-20/powell-inflation-has-eased-but-it-s-still-too-high-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:56:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储对餐饮业的影响：Lucques Group 的 Styne</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-20/fed-impact-on-restaurant-industry-caroline-styne-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lucques Group 联合创始人 Caroline Styne 表示，餐饮业感受到了美联储的影响，并希望看到美联储停止加息，并可能降低利率，因为外出就餐的价格正在上涨。她说，管理成本是一种平衡行为，而且极其困难。卡罗琳·斯泰恩 (Caroline Styne) 与凯蒂·格雷菲尔德 (Katie Greifeld) 就“彭博市场”进行对话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-20/fed-impact-on-restaurant-industry-caroline-styne-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:41:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍威尔表示放慢量化宽松步伐很快就会合适</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/fed-will-maintain-current-cadence-of-reducing-its-balance-sheet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储将维持减持债券的步伐，尽管官员们表示，尽快放慢减持步伐是适当的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/fed-will-maintain-current-cadence-of-reducing-its-balance-sheet</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:17:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储向市场保证 2024 年降息，短期债券上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/bonds-rally-after-fed-keeps-2024-median-rate-forecast-at-3-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储政策制定者坚持今年降息三个百分点的预测后，短期国债大幅上涨，消除了市场对美联储将限制宽松货币政策计划的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/bonds-rally-after-fed-keeps-2024-median-rate-forecast-at-3-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:13:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Astera IPO 融资 7.13 亿美元，人工智能需求飙升 76%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/astera-soars-46-after-713-million-ipo-snapped-up-on-ai-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者纷纷买入人工智能相关股票，半导体连接公司 Astera Labs Inc. 的首次公开募股超出了预期，筹集了 7.13 亿美元，其股价在首次交易中上涨了 76%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/astera-soars-46-after-713-million-ipo-snapped-up-on-ai-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
