      <title>巴西第二大银行表示卢拉已寻求帮助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/brazil-s-second-biggest-bank-says-lula-has-been-seeking-its-help</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西银行首席执行官塔西亚娜·梅代罗斯 (Tarciana Medeiros) 表示，巴西总统要求该国第二大银行加入政府的行列，帮助促进信贷和经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/brazil-s-second-biggest-bank-says-lula-has-been-seeking-its-help</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:51:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顶级高尔夫卡拉威否认销售谈判报道后削减涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/topgolf-callaway-soars-on-report-it-s-exploring-sale-spinoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[顶级高尔夫卡拉威品牌公司 (Topgolf Callaway Brands Corp.) 驳斥了早些时候的一份报道，该报道称该公司正在考虑出售其高尔夫装备部门，并表示不知道有任何出售该业务的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/topgolf-callaway-soars-on-report-it-s-exploring-sale-spinoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:22:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴货币因美联储预测和鲍威尔言论而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/emerging-market-currencies-extend-losses-before-fed-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场货币在七个交易日中首次上涨，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，较高的通胀预测不会破坏今年的降息计划，政策制定者坚持三次降息的预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/emerging-market-currencies-extend-losses-before-fed-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 10:10:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息押注导致收益率下降，标普 500 指数突破 5,200 点：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储维持 2024 年三次降息的预期，股市上涨，债券收益率下跌，杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示“在今年某个时候”开始宽松是合适的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 21:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
